#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:291
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The organization of the screen"
msgstr "Ikigo: Bya i Mugaragaza "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most important part of the editor is of course the editing area, this is "
"the area where you draw your regular expression. This area is the larger "
"gray one in the middle."
msgstr ""
"By'ingirakamaro Inzira %s Bya i Muhinduzi ni Bya i Guhindura Umwanya , iyi "
"ni i Umwanya Gushushanya Ibisanzwe imvugo . Umwanya ni i Kinini Ikigina "
"Rimwe in i Hagati . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Above the editing area you have two Toolbars, the first one contains the "
"<link linkend=\"editingtools\">editing actions</link> - much like drawing "
"tools in a drawing program. The second Toolbar contains the <emphasis>What's "
"This?</emphasis> button, and buttons for undo and redo."
msgstr ""
"i Guhindura Umwanya Kabiri , i Itangira Rimwe ifite i <link linkend="
"\"editingtools\"> Guhindura Ibikorwa </link> - nka Igishushanyo Ibikoresho "
"in A Igishushanyo Porogaramu . ISEGONDA ifite i <emphasis> iyi </emphasis> "
"Akabuto , na Utubuto ya:  Isubiranyuma na Gu&subiramo . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
